OL,3,CRoyal family gather in Cotswold
OL,4,Cvillage for wedding of Peter Phillips
OL,6,FA quiet village in the Cotswolds is
OL,7,Fhosting a royal wedding today as
OL,8,Fsenior members of the Royal Family
OL,9,Fcelebrate the marriage of Princess
OL,10,FAnne's son, Peter Phillips.
OL,12,FThe King and Queen, as well as the
OL,13,FPrince and Princess of Wales, are in
OL,14,Fthe congregation in Kemble near
OL,15,FCirencester.
OL,17,FIt is the second marriage for both
OL,18,FPeter Phillips and his bride, Harriet
OL,19,FSperling, who is a paediatric nurse in
OL,20,Fthe NHS.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
