OL,3,CRoyal family gather in Cotswold
OL,4,Cvillage for wedding of Peter Phillips
OL,6,FPeter's children from his first
OL,7,Fmarriage, Isla and Savannah, are the
OL,8,Fbridesmaids alongside Harriet
OL,9,FSperling's daughter, Georgina.
OL,11,FIt's a private ceremony inside All
OL,12,FSaints Church, but the arrival of so
OL,13,Fmany royals has attracted large crowds
OL,14,Fand dozens of photographers.
OL,16,FPrince William, who is Peter Phillips'
OL,17,Fcousin, and Kate are attending without
OL,18,Ftheir children.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
