OL,3,CRoyal family gather in Cotswold
OL,4,Cvillage for wedding of Peter Phillips
OL,6,FPeter's other cousins, Princesses
OL,7,FBeatrice and Eugenie, are guests, but
OL,8,FPrince Harry, another cousin, and
OL,9,FMeghan are not expected.
OL,11,FSources suggest Harry and Peter have
OL,12,Fnot stayed in touch since the Duke of
OL,13,FSussex moved to California.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
