OL,3,CRoyal family gather in Cotswold
OL,4,Cvillage for wedding of Peter Phillips
OL,6,FWhen he was born in 1977, Peter
OL,7,FPhillips, now 48, was the late Queen
OL,8,FElizabeth's first grandchild. His
OL,9,Fparents are the Princess Royal and her
OL,10,Fformer husband, Captain Mark Philips.
OL,12,FBoth parents will be at the church to
OL,13,Fsee their son get married, along with
OL,14,FPeter's stepfather, Vice Admiral Sir
OL,15,FTim Laurence.
OL,17,FThe location of the wedding is close
OL,18,Fto where Princess Anne and Sir Tim
OL,19,Flive at Gatcombe Park; Harriet's
OL,20,Fmother also lives in Gloucestershire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
