OL,3,CRoyal family gather in Cotswold
OL,4,Cvillage for wedding of Peter Phillips
OL,6,FPhillips and his first wife separated
OL,7,Fin 2020 after 12 years of marriage,
OL,8,Fand this service, in a small village
OL,9,Fchurch, is very different to his first
OL,10,Fwedding ceremony in 2008, in St
OL,11,FGeorge's Chapel in the grounds of
OL,12,FWindsor Castle.
OL,14,FHarriet Sperling was first linked to
OL,15,FMr Phillips in 2024, and at last
OL,16,Fyear's Royal Ascot, she was invited by
OL,17,Fthe King to ride in the official
OL,18,Fcarriage procession at the start of
OL,19,Fthe day's racing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
