OL,3,CRoyal family gather in Cotswold
OL,4,Cvillage for wedding of Peter Phillips
OL,6,FThe Gloucestershire wedding ceremony
OL,7,Fis the first of two appointments for
OL,8,FKing Charles and Queen Camilla on
OL,9,FSaturday, as they will head straight
OL,10,Fto the Epsom Derby in the afternoon
OL,11,Ffor the key racing event, where they
OL,12,Fwill present the trophy to the winning
OL,13,Fjockey.
OL,15,FThe bride will be escorted to the
OL,16,Fchurch by her brother, Nicholas, as
OL,17,Ftheir father has passed away.
OL,19,FThe mother-of-the-bride, Mary Sanders,
OL,20,Fwill be at the service with Harriet's
OL,21,Fother siblings, Louisa and Rebecca.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
